genresAdvancedInfo.name: denver rap
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Denver rap is a subgenre of hip-hop that originated in the city of Denver, Colorado. It is characterized by its heavy basslines, intricate rhymes, and socially conscious lyrics that often touch on themes of poverty, crime, and inequality. Denver rap has a unique sound that sets it apart from other regional styles, and it has gained a loyal following in recent years.
